Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.19,0:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,诺爱儿
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.97,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.05,0:00:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然都看不到人
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是发生了死神骚动...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.27,0:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,诚
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.38,0:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,诺爱儿发来的？
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.68,0:00:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我见到椿了哦 我们现在在一起
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.80,0:00:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和她谈谈
